### Products API - Servlet + JDBC

# ═══════════════════════════════════
# CRIAR PRODUTOS
# ═══════════════════════════════════

### Criar produto - Laptop
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop Gaming",
  "description": "High-end gaming laptop with RTX 4080",
  "price": 7500.00,
  "category": "Electronics"
}

###

